    <item>
      <title>哈利法克斯称英国房价自 2022 年以来涨幅最快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/uk-house-prices-up-at-strongest-pace-since-2022-halifax-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最大的抵押贷款机构之一表示，由于抵押贷款利率下降鼓励买家重返市场，英国房价以 2022 年中期以来最强劲的速度上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/uk-house-prices-up-at-strongest-pace-since-2022-halifax-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:10:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orsted 暂停派息，首席执行官试图削减不断上升的成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/orsted-pauses-dividend-as-ceo-cuts-costs-to-avoid-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Orsted A/S 将暂停支付股息，至少到 2025 年为止，并削减本十年建设新项目的计划，作为首席执行官 Mads Nipper 概述的一系列成本削减措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/orsted-pauses-dividend-as-ceo-cuts-costs-to-avoid-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:09:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TotalEnergies 提高股息，摆脱利润下降的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/totalenergies-raises-dividend-shrugging-off-drop-in-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TotalEnergies SE 提高了股息并继续股票回购，摆脱了石油和天然气价格疲软以及炼油利润下降导致的第四季度收益下降 31% 的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/totalenergies-raises-dividend-shrugging-off-drop-in-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:09:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着危机的消退，维斯塔斯今年的前景正在改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/vestas-posts-improving-outlook-for-this-year-as-crisis-abates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维斯塔斯风力系统公司 (Vestas Wind Systems A/S) 预计，随着这家丹麦公司扭转了导致项目开发放缓的全行业危机，在 2023 年恢复盈利后，今年的盈利将进一步改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/vestas-posts-improving-outlook-for-this-year-as-crisis-abates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Monte Paschi 誓言 13 年来首次派发股息，扭亏为盈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/paschi-vows-first-dividend-in-13-years-as-turnaround-pays-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[锡耶纳蒙特银行 (Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena SpA) 计划在中断 13 年之后支付首次股息，因为该银行的重组显示出成功的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/paschi-vows-first-dividend-in-13-years-as-turnaround-pays-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:43:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管利润下降，Equinor仍将向投资者支付140亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/equinor-profit-retreats-on-lower-prices-for-natural-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Equinor ASA 表示，今年将按照石油巨头向投资者分配剩余现金的现行做法，支付 140 亿美元的股票回购和股息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/equinor-profit-retreats-on-lower-prices-for-natural-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>1MDB 刑期减半后纳吉可能寻求全面赦免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/malaysia-s-najib-may-re-apply-for-full-pardon-on-1mdb-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚前领导人纳吉布·拉扎克的律师表示，在卸任国王将他的刑期减半后，他正在“认真考虑”再次申请赦免他与一马发展有限公司相关的定罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/malaysia-s-najib-may-re-apply-for-full-pardon-on-1mdb-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者等待更多政策支持，中国股市涨势放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/china-stock-rally-extends-as-policy-support-optimism-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市在前一交易日大幅上涨后，涨势放缓，凸显当局需要采取更有力的措施来维持刚刚起步的市场复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/china-stock-rally-extends-as-policy-support-optimism-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 01:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
